data.description: Very well maintained house in move in condition. Just pack you bags and move in. Enjoy finished basement with full bath. Second floor has nicely sized bedrooms with new bath and wood floor. Wall to Wall carpet is in the living room and steps. You will find this home to be warm and inviting. Close to transportation. Hurry! Hurry! It won~t last long!
